pageContext.claim: “Make sure you send the ballot in and then go to your polling place and make sure it counts, make sure it counts. Because the only way they can win is by doing very bad things, that's the only way.”
pageContext.analysis: Joe Biden has multiple paths to win the 2020 presidential election that do not require “doing very bad things.” Moreover, there is no evidence that voter fraud was likely to happen or did happen on Election Day.
